# Branch History Tab

Three complementary views: **Commit Graph** (commit-centric), **Branch Tracking** (sync-centric), **Branch History** (time-centric — one horizontal lane per branch).

Answers: which branches diverged/stale, where pushed vs unpushed, multi-remote divergence. Signature viz: **ghost track** under diverged lanes (faded default-branch progression since LCA).

## Data flow

```
App (tab=history) → request-branch-history { dateRange }
  → extension.loadBranchHistory → getBranchLifecycles()
  → branch-history-data { lifecycles, defaultBranch, remoteMains, window }
  → BranchHistoryTab → execute-branch-action (on success: reload branches/remotes/history/commits)
```

Messages/types: `BranchLifecycle`, `BranchHistoryPayload`, loading scope `branch-history` in `src/shared/types.ts`.

## Git layer

| Helper | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| `resolveDefaultBranch` | `origin/HEAD` symbolic ref → `main` → `master` → first local |
| `resolveHistoryDateWindow` | `presetDays: null` (All) **capped at 90d** — unlike graph unbounded All |
| `getBranchLifecycles` | local lifecycles + remote-only (`!localBranchName` from `getRemoteBranches`) |
| `computePerRemoteDivergence` | per-remote `{remote}/{defaultBranch}...branch` behind counts |
| `sortBranchLifecycles` | default → diverged (severe→high→mild) → active → remote-only → merged |

`branch-status.ts`: `detectStatus`, `generateDescription`, `STALE_THRESHOLD_DAYS = 7`.

### Status algorithm

| Status | Condition |
|--------|-----------|
| merged | tip is ancestor of default branch (wins over stale) |
| diverged mild | ahead>0 and behind 1–5 |
| diverged high | behind 6–12 |
| diverged severe | behind 13+ |
| active | behind=0 |
| remote-only | no local `refs/heads/<name>` |

**Stale** = secondary flag when `daysSinceActivity > 7` on non-merged locals — not a primary status.

## Tab behavior

- Lazy load: `request-branch-history` only when `tab === "history"` (not in `loadInitialData`).
- Shared `dateRange` across tabs; switching tabs does **not** reset it.
- First visit: if range still default `7d`, promote to `30d` once (`getState()` flag).
- Default selection: checked-out → first diverged → default branch.
- `.current` = checked out; `.selected` = detail/quick-actions target.

## Layout constants

| Element | Size |
|---------|------|
| Label column | `220px` (`LABEL_W`) |
| Detail panel | `320px` fixed (no splitter v1) |
| Right padding | `40px` (`PAD_R`) |
| Day column | **dynamic** — `DAY_W = (containerW - LABEL_W - PAD_R) / totalDays` via `ResizeObserver` |
| Normal lane | `72px` |
| Diverged lane | `96px` (`72 + DIV_GAP(14) + 10`) |
| Bar height | `8px` |
| Commit dot | scales with `DAY_W` — `max(2, min(3.5, DAY_W * 0.15))` (`3px` max on default branch) |

**No horizontal scrollbar.** Timeline SVG width equals measured container width; outer `.branch-history-timeline` uses `overflow: hidden`, inner scroll is vertical-only.

### Smart detail hiding (by `DAY_W`)

| Threshold | Effect |
|-----------|--------|
| `DAY_W ≤ 12` | Hide hash labels, LCA text, stale idle pill |
| `DAY_W ≤ 15` | Hide remote position markers |
| `DAY_W < 8` | Weekly labels ~monthly |
| `DAY_W < 15` | Weekly labels ~bi-weekly |
| `DAY_W < 25` | Weekly labels weekly |
| else | Label every Monday + first day |

Helpers: `src/webview/components/history/timelineLayout.ts`, hook `useTimelineLayout.ts`.

### Narrow pane safety

When `containerW < MIN_TIMELINE_WIDTH` (260px = `LABEL_W + PAD_R`), `computeTimelineTimeWidth()` clamps to `0` so `dayWidth` is never negative. Lanes compress into the label column until the pane widens (detail panel is fixed `320px`; timeline is `flex: 1`).

## Legend (`BranchHistoryTab`)

Status rows: Active, Diverged, Merged, Remote-only. Visual key (all via `useThemeColors()` / CSS classes — no hardcoded hex):

- **stale** tag sample (`.branch-history-stale-tag`)
- Filled commit dot + hollow main-ghost dot
- Main path swatch (default branch color, low opacity)
- Hash pill sample (`.branch-history-legend-hash`)
- Remote triangle (`remoteColor()`)

## Lane stale idle pill

When `branch.stale` and `DAY_W > 12`: SVG pill at `endX + 8` with `{idleDays}d idle` (`idleDays = todayDay - lastCommitDay`).

## Detail panel metrics

2×2 grid: Commits, Age, **Last active** (`Nd ago`), Status. Warn color on Last active uses **`branch.stale`** from the Git layer — do not duplicate `STALE_THRESHOLD_DAYS` in the webview.

- Time flows left→right; default branch topmost with thicker bar.
- Hash labels at both bar ends; remote triangle flags only when `behindLocal > 0`.
- Ghost track for **all diverged local** branches only.
- Three-tier gridlines: daily subtle, weekly labeled, Today accent.
- Remote-only: dashed bar, `remoteColor`, opacity ~0.35, no ghost track.
- Theme via `useThemeColors()` / `--sg-history-*`; no hardcoded hex in components.

## SVG rules — DO NOT

- Cross-lane fork/merge connector curves between lanes.
- Ghost track for active, merged, or remote-only lanes.
- Remote markers when fully pushed (`behindLocal = 0`).
- Use `stale` as primary status.
- Invalid SVG attrs like `color-mix` — use `fillOpacity` / `strokeOpacity`.

## Light theme

`body.vscode-light`: darken `--sg-history-*` tokens for contrast. Selected lane labels: `--selection-fg` on `.branch-history-lane-label.selected`. Raise label/hash/LCA opacity in `GhostTrack` / `BranchLane`.

